short_description: fred elevates™ is a business consulting company based in chicago, illinois, united states.
long_description:
fred elevates llc is a socially conscious digital empire founded by writer, life coach, solutionist, and serial entrepreneur fred t. williams. our mission is to empower people to grow better and do greater in every area and aspect of their life and business. we accomplish this through the convos podcast with fred t. williams, our various shows and vlogs on fred
tv, live events and seminars, working 1 on 1 with clients, as well as our online learning center better greater u.we believe that each person has the power to change the life of someone else in a meaningful way. this is why our efforts are focused on helping people become the best version of themselves in life and in business. this company was founded with one central idea: change the world. our mission is to impact 200 million lives. once we accomplish that, we'll go for 200 million more. we hire people who are motivated by our mission and passionate about creating positive change in the lives of others and our world as a whole. our team is remotely distributed; we care more about your work ethic and attitude than your location.
